This repository contains course-project modifications based on the open-source OpenLoong-Dyn-Control project.

Original project:

Name: OpenLoong-Dyn-Control / OpenLoong Dynamics Control
Repository: https://github.com/loongOpen/OpenLoong-Dyn-Control
License: Apache License 2.0
Original authors / operators: Humanoid Robotics (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Shanghai Humanoid Robotics Manufacturing Innovation Center, and OpenAtom Foundation, as stated by the upstream project.

This repository is not an official OpenLoong repository.

Modifications in This Repository

Course-project modifications include, but are not limited to:

Enhanced automatic obstacle avoidance demo
Virtual LiDAR scanning using MuJoCo ray casting
Low-obstacle step-over logic
High-obstacle bypass logic
Arc-length style waypoint tracking
Manual multi-function control mode
Additional MuJoCo simulation scenes
Foot-ground contact parameter adjustments
Fall detection and simulation reset logic
Additional demo and testing files
